OL,3,CWoman dies after being attacked by two
OL,4,Cdogs in Wolverhampton
OL,6,FA woman has died after being attacked
OL,7,Fby two dogs in at a house in
OL,8,FWolverhampton.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FWillis Pearson Avenue at around
OL,12,F11.30pm to reports a woman in her 70s
OL,13,Fwas being attacked by two dogs.
OL,15,FDespite the efforts of emergency
OL,16,Fservices, the woman sadly died at the
OL,17,Fscene.
